{"tid":2220323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動Post]十月一掛黑衫大行動","createTime":"2020-09-27T14:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T02:09:01.000Z","uid":107577,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"49ef983b552ba467d063721bd6a18544b3c075cd","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>香港人 Be Water<br />\n用傷亡最少嘅行動去表達意見</strong></span></span><br />\n十月一號係某大國國慶，香港人又係比某大國剝奪曬應有嘅權利，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>咁啱當日又有假放，係咪應該做D嘢？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">號召所有愛自由，愛民主嘅香港人十月一號一起洗衫！然後掛你件洗咗嘅衫出窗口！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n <span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>十月一 洗邋遢大行動日期：九月三十到十月一<br />\n細節：九月三十號日落之後將一件或多件嘅黑色衫掛出當眼處，例如：陽台，晾衫架，窗口，十月一號日落後收番所有衫<br />\n特殊情況：落雨嘅話就將黑色衫掛滿窗口<br />\n</strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n以行動話比全世界聽，我哋香港人係冇放棄，係一直都追求緊自由同民主！<br />\n<br />\n我哋要真普選，我哋要投票，我哋要民主！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YN5t8YM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYN5t8YM.jpg&h=4eb49fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjNXhR7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjNXhR7.jpg&h=e2fc13e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(有口號嘅靚衫要收埋先，狗狗見到上你屋企吠你就唔好啦)<br />\n(住狗狗宿舍或者附近嘅手足都唔好掛)<br />\n<br />\n風險問題：<br />\n我覺得風險算低<br />\n有口號嘅靚衫唔掛，住狗舍或者附近嘅手足唔掛<br />\n1.應該冇人會特意數你屋企位置<br />\n2.就算數，都唔知咩人住入面<br />\n3.就算知，都唔知你係咪咁啱洗黑衫<br />\n4.就算知你屋企位置，知咩人住入面，知你係黃絲，佢都奈何唔到你<br />\n5.更何況好多人一齊做<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>一齊掛，叫曬所有人一齊掛！</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1zrba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1zrba2.jpg&h=b001db63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白羅斯嘅朋友都用呢招！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TA6kZ4B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTA6kZ4B.jpg&h=35b07827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接連幾個禮拜我都會大力宣傳，希望多多支持<br />\nTg Channel (純粹發佈消息用)<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEcuHqz2znXG5EWzLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEcuHqz2znXG5EWzLw&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=155d9605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEcuHqz2znXG5EWzLw</a>"},{"pid":"6dcf5a5212b5d179167963626e9c4d468e665ee7","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"自推三十連"},{"pid":"3acda61ae46e5a55f65f70f82510e6fb50a79e97","tid":2220323,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"不推<br />\n咁咪好容易比敵人知我哋住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b900be0356210564ea7ae602c47fef02f6f8e7e5","tid":2220323,"uid":233905,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"都唔知咩人住入面<br />\n-你真係以為咁難查？公屋居屋要同政府申請 私人樓你買嗰陣又要同政府登記<br />\n直接自爆我哋咪冇咗隱蔽性"},{"pid":"cc5c5e1a8f2088d9dd834a85ddb73e57d0c1c59f","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3acda61ae46e5a55f65f70f82510e6fb50a79e97","tid":2220323,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"不推<br />\n咁咪好容易比敵人知我哋住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"風險問題小弟有講，希望解答到你嘅疑問"},{"pid":"c24e9eb97a58a678a134b38281b8f9731f9186b2","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b900be0356210564ea7ae602c47fef02f6f8e7e5","tid":2220323,"uid":233905,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"都唔知咩人住入面<br />\n-你真係以為咁難查？公屋居屋要同政府申請 私人樓你買嗰陣又要同政府登記<br />\n直接自爆我哋咪冇咗隱蔽性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"要達到以上條件<br />\n要有一隊人逐層樓數，數到你嗰層然後睇建築圖，確定你嘅方位後，再去稅局搵你個住址嘅資料<br />\n搵完之後先確定到你嘅資料，有你嘅資料之後都唔知搵咩罪入你<br />\n<br />\n當然你都可以話有風險，因為咩都可以用黨安法，係<br />\n但結論係風險極低"},{"pid":"bc605e8d1864afc14c03e07543997f9fd8b06daa","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"740d3fb02b6a30ae429751e249a22479eadd86e8","tid":2220323,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"211354e880f0d552bccf75ad949250502034e491","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30c51b0760c438c6381a0895ade7a4cfd5a57ce0","tid":2220323,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb65cac877543e4ed11fa18aadce787cd7bdbe2","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b8e33d4da46091f29b615afcac7e66dbdcc807f","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"682a6b424b48f74315078c3376e6da4011e78a81","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56718be257d90b0c1179c3ccaa2358d3a628da74","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57d618fc18618a5865b443cc08c03ecf45908576","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41ef1ab2293623473d505e399e386736baf11260","tid":2220323,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit